\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSg0OXbk.jpg&h=791a8ec6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ivfSEpG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FivfSEpG.jpg&h=e07fd1e0&s={SIZE}\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"94e4893d343023bf39245c8ded52ee341a54a76f","tid":2081820,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T13:49:55.000Z","msg":"另見<br />\n（！緊急！）根據連登網軍同熱普城派系kol嘅風向，我大概諗到中共對付初選嘅劇本<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2081264\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2081264</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}}